Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Exceeds... The only creatures in \NEdolas who have magic power inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason we couldn't use magic was \Nbecause of the unease in our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We have to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the legend says,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we knew that wizards from Earthland \Nhave magic power inside their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the Exceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:14.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that magic power cannot \Nbe compared to the Exceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that girl named Lucy also \Nhas magic power in her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then killing her is, whoa, such a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Irrelevant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have orders to eliminate her \Nfrom Queen Chagot of the Exceeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An order from the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot oppose the Exceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, whoa, it's such a waste! Dang, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it is still impossible with our \Ntechnology to extract magic power from human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what will we do with \Nthose two Dragon Slayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are human, and yet not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the experiment is a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we could get our hands on a \Nnear-infinite supply of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent, Byro. Begin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:25.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And just in case, speed up the magic power \Nextraction from the Earthland lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In just a bit, this world \Nmight get magic power back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do first, Sugar Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, Magic Surfing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna surf, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Panther Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, it is about the \Nrecent military buildup...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.  If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Code ETD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy and Carla are a race called the Exceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed... On this world, they're like angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And their Queen Chagot is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:40.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The word of God is law, and it \Nis her job to regulate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If her mouth says "die", that \Nhuman has no choice but to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous! How \Nunfair of a law can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've researched this \Nworld quite well, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you can still \Nput on such a brave face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand the \Nposition you are in, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face, your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like the Erza I know, so I \Ncouldn't help but feel a little at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earthland me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In our world, you're a member of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:47.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong, and cool... \Nand a little bit scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone really depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You also love sweets and cute clothes, \Nand are actually quite girly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No more talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not the Erza you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to save my friends, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be a different person, that's \Ntrue. But I can tell you're the same deep down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a person that can \Nlaugh at people's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza would never do this to \Nsomeone who wasn't resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She could never do this, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People's suffering is {\i1}my{\i0} favorite dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:07:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize why I'm called the Fairy Hunter? \NI've killed countless members of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say those things in \NErza's voice, with Erza's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything'll be okay! \NWe're here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your wings are back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it was a problem with our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, I misjudged and \Ngave it too much of a boost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This individual was ordered \Nto be eliminated by the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The order has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it comes directly from an Exceed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't have the authority \Nto reverse an order from the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hand that woman over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human, know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn who stands before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is I, Princess Carla, \Ndaughter of Queen Chagot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Wen- are the two Dragon Slayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The basement of the west tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not have the authority to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, those two Exceeds are Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been chased out of Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that? An ally of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any Exceeds \Nthat were all buff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, weren't you a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alert all the troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Fallen have escaped with a prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fallen Exceeds are blue and white!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate them on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our fault that you were caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you went and saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm not angry one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm shocked to hear you're \Nthe daughter of the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a bluff, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you making that face, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just thought, "That's \Nthe Carla I know."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did she just call him Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:13.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, you. Right now, we \Nhave to hurry and find Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The west tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said the two were being \Nheld in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you smiling about, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the west tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found you, Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a flock of cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's land on solid ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's enemies on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, what about your Celestial Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:58.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This sticky stuff seems to block my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Extalia Royal Guard has \Ncome chasing after two Fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Code ETD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Code ETD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 10-12, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,14 and 15, all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,6-9, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He activated the Territorial Security\N Last Defense Operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head inside a building!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Code ETD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What devilry is this, humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they aiming at the Exceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceeds are like angels \Nor gods to humans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a rebellion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know, but it seems like our \Nbest course of action is to use the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go save Wendy and Natsu \Nwhile we have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The Fallen and the prisoner have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be heading toward the west tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Double up the defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen will not stay silent on this! Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exceeds turned into a lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've really done it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no gods in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only we humans suffer \Nfrom limited magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the while, the Exceed revel \Nin their infinite magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can we not obtain that \Ninfinity so near to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I proclaim the end to the \Nera where we are controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for the future of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For creating a prosperous magic society!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:14:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers, stand with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Code ETD: Exceed Total Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate operation Extermination of Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, things just got real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is why he was \Nbuilding up the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can steal the Exceeds' magic power, \Nour kingdom can obtain an infinite supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, the Queen is coming to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The military might of Extalia is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I captured the Dragon Slayers \Nprecisely for this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time we must cast down the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and extract their Dragon Slayer Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two prepared for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have really gotten crazy, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that the humans and \Nthe Exceeds have started a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have anything to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both the same! They can \Nfight all they want, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be going any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For goodness sake! Weren't you \Ngoing to leave us alone for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You took a direct hit from my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this will be your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never received an order \Nto capture you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strike the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:43.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I'm sorry... I was so \Nclose to saving you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:47.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this is as far as I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:53.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's me. And Natsu is there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:59.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Natsu would \Nnever give up, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayers are impressive, indeed... \NBoth of you have considerable magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And don't you dare give up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of this, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:55.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure our friends will come for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you don't know when to quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that part of the toughness \Nof being a Dragon Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:17.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Don't you ever give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up it'll be your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I'll give you my \Nmagic power in Wendy's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not here. Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:37.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're basically completely trapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably a very tight \Nguard around Wendy and Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we wanted to, we couldn't get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we made it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu never gave up, no matter what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's made it this far by always \Nfighting through to the end! {talking about Natsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's our turn to learn from Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some kind of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the blue Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my Poison Mist attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't inhale it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid! It's just flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, you'd better escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:13.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have one sacrifice himself, and rescue \Nthem when the guard is weakened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would try something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you \Ndoing to Natsu and Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:33.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stealing the magic power \Nwe need for Code ETD from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:48.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your devil's luck just ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Wendy back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a hand on Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then. I'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this knowing they're \Nmembers of our guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will never forgive those who lay \Nhands on our fellow guild members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are now our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey... What the heck's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so shaken up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two Erzas, and what's \Nmore, they're fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. You didn't know, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he'll listen to a thing I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Erza vs. Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being shaken up sure works up an appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!!
